    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concluded that the Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification and the breadth of factors assessed collectively support a High assurance level. The panel noted that absolute hemolysis predictions were within an order of magnitude of experimental measurements and that the software quality assurance gaps are considered manageable given the maturity of the CFD platform. Decision recorded as Accepted with High assurance.",
